# Easy Daily Tools - Date Utilities Collection

A collection of free online date calculators to help you plan, calculate, and organize time easily.  
These tools are useful for students, professionals, and anyone who needs quick answers for scheduling.

---

## 1. Date Difference Calculator
The **Date Difference Calculator** helps you find out how many days are between two dates.  
This is useful when calculating project deadlines, tracking events, or simply checking how long until a special day.

