## 2. Date Add & Subtract Calculator
The **Date Add & Subtract Calculator** lets you quickly add or subtract days, weeks, months, or years from a specific date.  
Perfect for planning due dates, calculating maturity periods, or tracking time-sensitive projects.

ðŸ‘‰ Try it here: [Date Add/Subtract Calculator](https://www.easydailytools.com/en/date-add-subtract-calculator)

**Features:**
- Add/subtract days, weeks, months, or years  
