## 4. Workday Calculator
The **Workday Calculator** allows you to calculate the number of business days between two dates, excluding weekends and optional holidays.  
Ideal for professionals, HR departments, and project managers who need accurate work schedules.

ðŸ‘‰ Try it here: [Workday Calculator](https://www.easydailytools.com/en/workday-calculator)

